No. 1, World’s Most Admired Company in Health Care: Pharmacy and Other Services category, Fortune, 2015.[33]
No. 22, The World's Most Innovative Companies, Forbes, 2014.[34]
UX Award, 2013, Best Clinical Health Care Experience, Powerchart Touch[35][36]


